<!-- A history page of Dunshaughlin written to include JS elements to make the page 
    interactive instead of just blocks of text. The buttons reveal the answers stored here
    with another button at the very end of the page calling to a button that will reset the
    answers to their initial ??? text -->

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Dunshaughlin - History</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="flex-fill container">
      <h1 class="mb-4">History of Dunshaughlin</h1>

      <!-- SECTION LOOP EXAMPLE -->
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="historySection p-4 mb-3 rounded">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/images/hist01.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="A picture of a statue of St. Seachnaill.">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Early Christian Roots</h3>
            <p>Dunshaughlin, known in Irish as Domhnach Seachnaill, traces its origins back to the 5th century when St. Seachnall founded a church here, one of the earliest in Ireland. The town grew around this religious site, which gave it both its name and cultural importance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Question + Answer Row -->
        <div class="row g-2 align-items-center mt-3 flex-wrap">
          <p class="col-12 text-center fw-bold mb-2">Question: What does "Domhnach Seachnaill" mean?</p>
          <div class="col-auto mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-primary qa-btn" data-qa-target="ans1" data-answer="It means 'the church of Seachnall'.">Reveal Answer</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div id="ans1" class="alert alert-primary mb-0">???</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="historySection p-4 mb-3 rounded">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
            <img src="/images/hist02.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="A video of the old Church and old ruins in Dunshaughlin.">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <h3>Medieval Growth</h3>
            <p>By the medieval period, Dunshaughlin had grown into a settlement of significance, complete with a marketplace and religious institutions. Its location along important travel routes made it a natural hub for commerce.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-2 align-items-center mt-3 flex-wrap">
          <p class="col-12 text-center fw-bold mb-2">Question: Why was Dunshaughlin a natural hub for commerce?</p>
          <div class="col-auto mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-primary qa-btn" data-qa-target="ans2" data-answer="Because of its location along important travel and trade routes.">Reveal Answer</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div id="ans2" class="alert alert-primary mb-0">???</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div class="historySection p-4 mb-3 rounded">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/images/hist03.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="An image of the Workhouse, one of the first big builds in Dunshaughlin.">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>18th & 19th Century Developments</h3>
            <p>During the 18th and 19th centuries, Dunshaughlin remained a rural market town. The construction of better roads and its role as a local fair site sustained its economic and social activity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-2 align-items-center mt-3 flex-wrap">
          <p class="col-12 text-center fw-bold mb-2">Question: What sustained Dunshaughlin's growth during this period?</p>
          <div class="col-auto mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-primary qa-btn" data-qa-target="ans3" data-answer="Road building and regular fairs sustained growth.">Reveal Answer</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div id="ans3" class="alert alert-primary mb-0">???</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div class="historySection p-4 mb-3 rounded">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
            <img src="/images/hist04.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Image of school children as Dunshaughlin continues to grow.">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <h3>20th Century Transformation</h3>
            <p>In the 20th century, Dunshaughlin evolved into a commuter town, with its proximity to Dublin leading to population growth and the development of new housing and schools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-2 align-items-center mt-3 flex-wrap">
          <p class="col-12 text-center fw-bold mb-2">Question: Why did Dunshaughlin grow in the 20th century?</p>
          <div class="col-auto mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-primary qa-btn" data-qa-target="ans4" data-answer="Its proximity to Dublin encouraged commuter settlement.">Reveal Answer</button>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div id="ans4" class="alert alert-primary mb-0">???</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <div class="historySection p-4 mb-3 rounded">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="/images/hist05.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Image of Modern Day Dunshaughlin.">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Modern Dunshaughlin</h3>
            <p>Today, Dunshaughlin is a vibrant and growing town with schools, businesses, and sports clubs. It balances its rich history with the demands of modern life, remaining an attractive place to live.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-2 align-items-center mt-3 flex-wrap">
          <p class="col-12 text-center fw-bold mb-2">Question: What characterizes modern Dunshaughlin?</p>
          <div class="col-auto mb-2">
